---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <img src="/about.png" alt="Morten and Anders" />
  <section class="intro">
    <p class="title">ABOUT</p>
    <h1>Twoeighty <br />production co.</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="grid_1">
    <article class="who">
      <h3>Who is 280</h3>
      <p>
        We, Morten and Anders, are a Copenhagen‐based duo with over a decade of experience in creative direction, film production, and still imagery. From intimate branded shorts to large‐scale campaigns, we thrive on transforming bold ideas into
        compelling visual narratives. Having collaborated with both local artisans and global corporations, we’ve learned to balance high‐level strategy with hands‐on execution—whether that means sketching storyboards over coffee or fine-tuning
        camera settings at dawn.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="philosophy">
      <h3>Our philosophy</h3>
      <p>
        At our core lies a belief in the power of genuine human stories. We don’t just make images; we seek out the thoughts, emotions, and subtle moments that resonate beneath the surface. Every project begins with listening—understanding what moves
        you, what challenges you, and what makes your brand unique. From there, we craft honest, relevant narratives that connect people to people, not just products to pixels. Authenticity for us isn’t a trend—it’s the only way to create work that
        truly matters.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="services">
      <h2>Twoeighty's</h2>
      <p class="title">SERVICES</p>
    </div>
    <section class="background">
      <div class="slider-container">
        <div class="slider-track">
          <img src="/banner/commercials.png" alt="Television commercials" />
          <img src="/banner/content.png" alt="Content creation" />
          <img src="/banner/corporate.png" alt="Corporate videos" />
          <img src="/banner/creative.png" alt="Creative direction" />
          <img src="/banner/filmproduction.png" alt="Creative film production" />
          <img src="/banner/interviews.png" alt="High end interviews" />
          <img src="/banner/photograph.png" alt="Lifestyle photography" />

          <img src="/banner/commercials.png" alt="Television commercials" />
          <img src="/banner/content.png" alt="Content creation" />
          <img src="/banner/corporate.png" alt="Corporate videos" />
          <img src="/banner/creative.png" alt="Creative direction" />
          <img src="/banner/filmproduction.png" alt="Creative film production" />
          <img src="/banner/interviews.png" alt="High end interviews" />
          <img src="/banner/photograph.png" alt="Lifestyle photography" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="grid_2">
      <div class="clients">
        <h4>Selected <br />clients</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Adidas</li>
          <li>Arbejdstilsynet</li>
          <li>Arbejdernes</li>
          <li>Landsbank</li>
          <li>CPH Airport</li>
          <li>Coca Cola</li>
          <li>Deloitte</li>
          <li>DJØF</li>
          <li>Danish Design Center</li>
          <li>Fitness World</li>
          <li>Fritz Hansen</li>
          <li>Microsoft</li>
          <li>Norwegian Airlines</li>
          <li>Topdanmark</li>
          <li>Spangsberg Flødeboller</li>
          <li>Wonderful Copenhagen</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="agencies">
        <h4>Selected <br /> agencies</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>BoyeSpellerberg</li>
          <li>CoPlus</li>
          <li>GeelmuydenKiese</li>
          <li>Lead Agency</li>
          <li>Mindshare</li>
          <li>Marvelous</li>
          <li>Sunrise</li>
          <li>Precis Digital</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="contact">
        <h4>Contact us</h4>
        <p>mail: info@280.dk</p>
        <p>phone: +45 31 46 20 10</p>
      </div>
      <button onclick="window.location.href='/contact.astro'" class="corner-button">
        <span class="corner top-left"></span>
        <span class="corner top-right"></span>
        <span class="corner bottom-left"></span>
        <span class="corner bottom-right"></span>
        GET IN TOUCH
      </button>
    </section>

    <style>
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .title {
        text-align: center;
      }

      main {
        margin: 10%;
      }
      .grid_1 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      }

      .who {
        grid-column: 1 / span 5;
        grid-row: 1;
      }

      .philosophy {
        grid-column: 2 / span 5;
        grid-row: 2;
      }

      .corner-button {
        position: relative;
        background: transparent;
        border: none;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 7px 9px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-right: 30px;
      }

      .corner {
        position: absolute;
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        border: 1.5px solid black;
      }

      .top-left {
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        border-right: none;
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .top-right {
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        border-left: none;
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .bottom-left {
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        border-right: none;
        border-top: none;
      }

      .bottom-right {
        bottom: 0;
        right: 0;
        border-left: none;
        border-top: none;
      }

      ul,
      p {
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .grid_2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .services {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .full_width {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: auto;
      }

      .background {
        background-color: black;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: 310px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .slider-container {
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .slider-track {
        display: flex;
        width: max-content;
        animation: scroll 15s linear infinite;
      }
      .slider-track img {
        width: 10em;
        padding-left: 0.6em;
        height: auto;
      }

      @keyframes scroll {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</Layout>
